data.description: Priced to sell quickly. This is a solidly built house in a great neighborhood. 2274 sqf with 3 bedrooms and 2.5 baths on the main level and a large bonus room over the garage. There is also a large covered front porch and a large rear cover porch. The neighborhood is immaculate with a very large center common area, club house and pool. Great location in the center of everything you need. Ask your Realtor for pictures of the inside of the house. Needs repairs. Great opportunity for someone. After repair value should be around $350k. Quotes on hand to repair at a cost of around $35k to $40k. If financing, may need a FHA 203k loan, otherwise cash only. Sold As-Is.
